{"tid":49992,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚call uber連cut 兩單","createTime":"2016-12-22T06:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T15:10:44.000Z","uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7e311ad578916c5e5a69a9cb5771c1a0952368","tid":49992,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:06:34.000Z","msg":"事源係咁<br />\n琴晚想話去個fd到<br />\n又唔想逼就諗住call uber啦<br />\n第一單 見十幾分鐘先到<br />\n我見之前啲巴打話其實好快就到<br />\n咁就等啦 過左一分鐘到司機打黎話仲係好遠 不如你cut單搵第架 咁我就話咁好啦 麻煩曬你 咁就cut左一單<br />\n然後當然再call啦<br />\n今次司機係附近實冇死一定上到車<br />\n跟住佢就打黎同我講<br />\n你好啊請問你係咪call uber<br />\n佢問我想去邊 <br />\n我話係啊 我想由旺角 搭入 荃灣<br />\n佢就同我講我岩岩定左位入屯門喎<br />\n<br />\n我因為唔知佢嗡乜<br />\n我就話 我想入荃灣 咁你既意思係？<br />\n佢load左一陣 跟住叫我cut單<br />\n<br />\n咁其實姐係咩意思<br />\n算唔算係揀客？<br />\n連call兩架都叫我cut單我又唔係唔等你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打知咩事可以解釋下"},{"pid":"5a89d992f1fea57c638cfcc093bfdbcc02c00691","tid":49992,"uid":6324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:08:57.000Z","msg":"Cut單要唔要俾錢"},{"pid":"07654bfaac4b32cdc4d76c226b6c031032ad19c6","tid":49992,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:09:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc559444888a78188a8e46ad84fcd83e635111fb","tid":49992,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:11:09.000Z","msg":"投訴囉，會有Coupon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111f7225a83392aae09fd2b182470b1bbf9f5f20","tid":49992,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:12:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cut單要唔要俾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n信用卡sd左sms黎扣30<br />\n但睇返好似冇扣到"},{"pid":"c7a8d5e016cc0cef850c9183037f9ec3f7f70435","tid":49992,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>投訴囉，會有Coupon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想知佢地有咩苦衷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無啦啦投訴人好on9"},{"pid":"dcaf89b304803baea65da601284bf65704e5e01e","tid":49992,"uid":64911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:24:51.000Z","msg":"可能太近"},{"pid":"d9bbedd836de46def193f9834a2f31f9471ebfa3","tid":49992,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:35:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能太近</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n旺角去荃灣近深井個邊都算近？<br />\nBtw我都唔知咩玩法<br />\n雖然唔趕時間<br />\n但好似俾人嫌咁"},{"pid":"7deebdfcc780eb6cc6e58511a926167bb4c2a1d7","tid":49992,"uid":65470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:38:23.000Z","msg":"駛乜理佢<br />\n叫佢跟UBER個APP行<br />\n除非係你自己SET錯左目的地<br />\n你一日未上車佢都唔會知你去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e7ae8df862156d8b4d336a01db1d6e55e3b6b5","tid":49992,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>駛乜理佢<br />\n叫佢跟UBER個APP行<br />\n除非係你自己SET錯左目的地<br />\n你一日未上車佢都唔會知你去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我直接係目的地打荃灣深井<br />\n但佢set左去屯門<br />\n其實係咩玩法"},{"pid":"141af0e365096d1e70b45351e3c89545bbbf523d","tid":49992,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:46:40.000Z","msg":"唔好係電話答佢去邊"},{"pid":"fae2e386a62ac95c1a0b48c21338a9134293fbff","tid":49992,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>投訴囉，會有Coupon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想知佢地有咩苦衷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無啦啦投訴人好on9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實最撚刻薄係Uber垃圾公司。<br />\n講真，成撚日派單派啲客距離其實都幾撚遠，但都局住要去接，大佬去接果程唔洗本咩。Uber收佣又收得多，基本上Uber司機賺既係少過的士好撚多。<br />\n<br />\n利申唔係司機但識人係"},{"pid":"796e21bd0cbc93f89085aef535dad142630952ca","tid":49992,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:50:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>駛乜理佢<br />\n叫佢跟UBER個APP行<br />\n除非係你自己SET錯左目的地<br />\n你一日未上車佢都唔會知你去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我直接係目的地打荃灣深井<br />\n但佢set左去屯門<br />\n其實係咩玩法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢吹既姐，未開始行程佢都唔知你去邊"},{"pid":"729a3b9f96b1cc84893703d67ca127dad0efac2a","tid":49992,"uid":10703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:51:20.000Z","msg":"試過零晨係機場call車，call左幾次都無車<br />\n最後有個司機接左，但要求我cut uber張單offline俾錢佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得uber做大左之後，司機質素愈來愈參差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65967af7fbd622841ca15eaa458a6724b202fbca","tid":49992,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:51:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過零晨係機場call車，call左幾次都無車<br />\n最後有個司機接左，但要求我cut uber張單offline俾錢佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得uber做大左之後，司機質素愈來愈參差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢收現金既話你報警"},{"pid":"6b7c15243ec133994ae195bc83b12daafd1c87f2","tid":49992,"uid":65470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:52:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>投訴囉，會有Coupon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想知佢地有咩苦衷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無啦啦投訴人好on9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實最撚刻薄係Uber垃圾公司。<br />\n講真，成撚日派單派啲客